import PopupWithForm from "../PopapWithForm/PopupWithForm";

export default function AddPlacePopup(isOpen, onClose, onUpdateAvatar){

    return(
        <PopupWithForm
        name="add-Card"
        title="Новое место"
        btnTitle="Добавить"
        isOpen={isAddPlacePopupOpen}
        onClose={CloseAllPopup}
      >
        <fieldset className="popup__elements">
          <input
            className="popup__element"
            type="text"
            name="title"
            id="title"
            placeholder="Название"
            minLength={2}
            maxLength={30}
            required=""
          />
          <span className="popup__error popup__error_type_title" />
          <input
            className="popup__element"
            type="url"
            name="link"
            id="link"
            placeholder="Ссылка на картинку"
            required=""
          />
          <span className="popup__error popup__error_type_link" />
        </fieldset>
      </PopupWithForm>
    )
}
